Slurm

```json
{
  "application": "Slurm",
  "details": {
    "job_name": "cs3730-dataset",
    "output": "output/%x-%A.out",
    "mail_user": "alc307@pitt.edu",
    "mail_type": ["END", "FAIL"],
    "cluster": "gpu",
    "partition": "a100",
    "constraint": "amd",
    "nodes": 1,
    "gres": "gpu:1",
    "ntasks_per_node": 1,
    "time": "5-00:00:00",
    "qos": "short",
    "modules": ["gcc/8.2.0", "python/anaconda3.10-2022.10"],
    "conda_environment": "cs3730",
    "python_script": "dataset.py",
    "arguments": "-d opus_books opus_wikipedia -s train -sl en -tl es -op 1 -b 128 -o datasets/opus -lo logs",
    "additional_scripts": ["crc-job-stats"]
  }
}
```
